public class XmlToDataObjectConvertor
extends AbstractLegacyConvertor

Convert XML into DataObjects Note: Usage of this class depends on the availability of a legacy openadaptor jar to do the conversions, as openadaptor 3 doesn't directly support dataobjects, or DOXML.
